@node "Games-Review-Olofight" "Olofight"
@toc "Games Reviews INDEX"


 -----------------------------------------
 - @{fg shine}REVIEW: OLOFIGHT@{fg text}                      -
 -                                       -
 - @{b}Style: Beat em Up@{ub}                     -
 -                                       -
 - @{b}Hersteller: The Real Ologram@{ub}          -
 -                                       -
 - @{b}Preis: ca.60 DM@{ub}                       -
 -                                       -
 - @{b}Benötigt: AGA,3MB RAM,FESTPLATTE@{ub}      -
 -                                       -
 - @{b}Empfohlen: 68030 PROZESSOR,FASTRAM@{ub}    -
